\&  my $dtd = $doc->internalSubset;
.Ve
.Sp
If a document has an internal subset defined it will be returned by this
function.
.Sp
\&\s-1NOTE\s0 Dtd nodes are no ordinary nodes in libxml2. The support for these nodes in
