\&  my @nodelist = $doc->getElementsByTagName($tagname);
.Ve
.Sp
Implements the \s-1DOM\s0 Level 2 function
.Sp
In \s-1SCALAR\s0 context this function returns a XML::LibXML::NodeList object.
